&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Project financial results and company revenue based on KPI data and business dynamics&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Review all client-facing reporting for accuracy, including reports on&lt;/span&gt;
